- There is also ╬Ę-reduction for structures:
  if `p : ŌäĢ ├Ś ŌäĢ` then `(p.1, p.2) ŌēĪ p`
- Proof irrelevance: if `h1, h2 : P` and `P : Prop` then `h1 ŌēĪ h2`.
